WEBVTT

00:00:01.400 --> 00:00:04.200
Today, guess what!

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:07.400
We're at the Fantasy Springs Hotel!

00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:09.100
Yay~!

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:13.200
We actually took a sneak peek earlier.

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:16.000
Today, the hotel we'll be staying at...

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.500
...is what we're going to show you!

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:19.800
Room tour!

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:21.000
Wow, I'm getting excited.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:23.700
Room tour, start!

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:25.500
Okay, Maika,

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:26.500
go ahead.

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:28.000
First of all...

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:32.500
Ta-da!

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:34.000
The living room?

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:36.000
Crazy, it's so spacious!

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:37.000
So spacious!

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:39.000
It's seriously amazing.

00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:42.000
First, um...

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:44.000
Where to first?

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.000
Uh... the bedroom.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:48.000
Please show us the bedroom.

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:51.500
Woooah!

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:53.000
This is incredible!

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:55.500
Eh, a princess?

00:00:55.500 --> 00:00:56.500
What's this?

00:00:56.500 --> 00:00:58.500
Um, I've become a princess.

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:00.000
Who's sleeping where today?

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:01.500
Where do you want to sleep?

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:05.000
We're usually not too picky about it, right?

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.500
But I think I'm usually on the inner side.

00:01:07.500 --> 00:01:08.500
You are, huh.

00:01:08.500 --> 00:01:12.500
Usually we're both pretty easygoing,
anywhere is fine.

00:01:12.500 --> 00:01:13.500
That's true.

00:01:13.500 --> 00:01:15.000
We're mostly together at hotels too.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:16.000
(Conclusion: either is fine for both of us)

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.500
Wait, there are two TVs!?

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:19.000
Eh, wait!?

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:20.500
There's one over here too, right?

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:22.500
So you can watch over there,
and I'll watch here... like that.

00:01:22.500 --> 00:01:24.000
That works.

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:26.000
I am Yamamoto the bellboy.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:28.000
Next, I'll introduce this area.

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:33.500
Where's the light switch~?

00:01:33.500 --> 00:01:35.000
You can see my reflection.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:36.500
Eh! Eh, look, it's so cool.

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:40.500
The door is also amazing.

00:01:40.500 --> 00:01:43.000
Um, where's the light switch for this?

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:47.000
How do we turn on the lights here?

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:49.000
It should... turn on from here, right?

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:51.500
Eh, there's no switch. Oh, wait, there is.

00:01:51.500 --> 00:01:53.000
Ah! It's on!

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:56.000
It's on. It's on.

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:57.000
We don't need this, do we?

00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:58.500
This is basically a castle.

00:01:58.500 --> 00:02:00.000
Look at this. We won't have to fight over it.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:02.500
We have two sinks!

00:02:03.500 --> 00:02:05.500
Crazy. It's so cool, right?

00:02:06.500 --> 00:02:08.500
Let's take a peek in here.

00:02:08.500 --> 00:02:10.000
Yes, please open it.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:11.000
Excuse me.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:18.000
There's a beautiful painting.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:20.000
Wow! It's so elegant.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:25.500
We just got back from Disneyland today and
our feet are so sore, so...

00:02:25.500 --> 00:02:29.000
we're going to soak in this bathtub,

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:31.500
while getting a massage, to prepare for Disney Sea tomorrow.

00:02:31.500 --> 00:02:33.500
Let's enjoy!

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:36.000
Look at this! Look at this!

00:02:36.500 --> 00:02:38.000
So cool! We can feel like princesses.

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:40.000
It's awesome to do our makeup here.

00:02:40.500 --> 00:02:42.500
Now, for the moment you've been waiting for...

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:44.500
What's it called again...?

00:02:44.500 --> 00:02:46.500
The main dish.

00:02:47.500 --> 00:02:50.000
For all of you, the view from this hotel...

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:51.500
...we're going to show it to you!

00:02:51.500 --> 00:02:54.000
Since the park is already closed,

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:01.000
We can't really see it yet, though.

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:03.000
That's our reflection. Our reflection.

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:08.000
Should we go out now? Let's go out.

00:03:18.500 --> 00:03:20.000
This is insane.

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:21.000
It's so beautiful.

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:23.000
It's so beautiful.

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:24.000
So beautiful, we can see it clearly.

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:27.000
It's so cool.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:31.500
We really feel like princesses right now.

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:33.500
Craaaazy!

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:35.500
Crazy.

00:03:35.500 --> 00:03:37.000
We're princesses.

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:41.500
It feels like we're already inside Disney Sea.

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:44.000
It's just one step away.

00:03:46.500 --> 00:03:49.000
We went to Disneyland on the first day, so...

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:51.500
here are the souvenirs...

00:03:51.500 --> 00:03:54.000
Not really souvenirs, but...
things I wanted to buy for myself...

00:03:55.500 --> 00:03:56.500
I bought these.

00:03:56.500 --> 00:03:59.000
Let's do a shopping haul.

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:02.000
This.

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:05.000
Churros Snack, Creme Brulee flavor.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:06.500
Looks delicious.

00:04:06.500 --> 00:04:10.500
This is for me, for Anna, and for the members.

00:04:12.500 --> 00:04:14.500
I love it so much.

00:04:14.500 --> 00:04:16.000
This is seriously so good.

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:17.500
I really love this.

00:04:17.500 --> 00:04:20.000
I've always bought this since way back.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:21.000
Yeah, it totally gives off your vibe.

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:23.000
But the packaging changes sometimes,

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:26.000
Wasn't it not Creme Brulee flavor before?

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:28.000
Yeah, what was it?
I think it was cinnamon flavor before.

00:04:26.500 --> 00:04:28.500
* There used to be a cinnamon flavor too!

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:31.000
Maybe this is my first time trying this one! Can't wait.

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:34.000
Little Green Men.

00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:38.500
You look just like a YouTuber.

00:04:38.500 --> 00:04:41.500
Cup... cup noodles.

00:04:41.500 --> 00:04:44.500
Because it looks cute.

00:04:44.500 --> 00:04:48.000
The noodles are green.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:49.000
It makes me really want to eat it.

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:51.500
When she found it earlier, she immediately said "I want this too!"

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:56.500
It's been so long since I've been here.
It's been a while since I went to Disney, and...

00:04:56.500 --> 00:04:58.000
shopping at Disney is also rare, right?

00:04:58.000 --> 00:04:59.000
We bought so much today.

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:01.000
Since we're adults now...

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:04.000
Oh yeah, the theme of our Disney trip this time...

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:06.000
...is "Disney for Adults".

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.000
We went around with that theme in mind.

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:10.000
That's why we were really taking it easy today.

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:11.500
But we rode quite a few attractions, right?

00:05:11.500 --> 00:05:14.500
Quite a lot, actually. Maybe because it's a weekday,

00:05:14.500 --> 00:05:17.500
it wasn't too crowded, so we got to ride a lot.

00:05:17.500 --> 00:05:22.000
We even got to try rides that we usually rarely
or never ride.

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:23.000
It was so much fun.

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:25.000
The canoes~

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:28.000
We rode the canoes, you know,

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:30.000
it was seriously so exhausting, right?

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.000
I swear it was so tiring.

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:34.000
So, the staff members there...

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:36.000
Yeah, the ones guiding the boat.

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:38.000
They're doing it all day long...

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:40.000
...rowing for so many laps, right.

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:42.000
They're all so muscular! I was amazed.

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:44.000
Halfway through, the two of us were just like...

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:46.000
"Do your best," ...like that.

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:48.000
What did we ride after that? The ship.

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:50.000
The ship. That big three-story ship, right?

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:52.000
Yeah. We rode that last.

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:54.000
Yeah. It was fun riding the relaxing ones.

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:56.000
Normally, we usually ride roller coasters.

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:58.500
Yeah, yeah. Thrill rides.

00:05:58.500 --> 00:06:01.000
Or the character-themed rides.

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:02.500
Those are what we ride most often,

00:06:02.500 --> 00:06:05.500
but since we're adults now, taking a relaxing walk
while enjoying the scenery...

00:06:07.500 --> 00:06:11.000
...or stopping by a restaurant to eat, feels different.

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:13.500
It really feels like we're adults.

00:06:13.500 --> 00:06:16.000
It felt really nice.
Because there were so many students on a school trip earlier.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:18.000
Yeah, they were all so cute.

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:19.500
So cute.

00:06:19.500 --> 00:06:22.500
During middle school, my school trip was also to Disney.

00:06:22.500 --> 00:06:24.000
So it felt super nostalgic.

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:26.000
It makes me want to wear a school uniform to Disney.

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:27.500
Oh, I'd love to do that!!!

00:06:27.500 --> 00:06:29.500
Unfortunately, we can't pull it off anymore.

00:06:29.500 --> 00:06:31.000
Wanna try? We can't.

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:34.000
This time it's Adult Disney. Next theme is Student Disney?

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:36.500
Returning to our youth.

00:06:36.500 --> 00:06:38.000
Next.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:40.500
Which one should I show. Oh, this one.

00:06:40.500 --> 00:06:42.500
Ta-da.

00:06:42.500 --> 00:06:45.000
★ Vanellope's Sweet Pop World (Cookies)

00:06:42.500 --> 00:06:45.000
Ta-da, cookies.

00:06:45.000 --> 00:06:46.500
So cute!

00:06:46.500 --> 00:06:48.000
I bought this purely because the packaging is cute.

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:50.000
It looks like a giant candy, so adorable.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:53.000
Ah, right! Let's take this off.

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:54.500
They look similar, right?

00:06:54.500 --> 00:06:56.500
Ta-da.

00:06:56.500 --> 00:06:59.000
These ears we wore at Disneyland are from the Pal-Palooza event,

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:01.000
...these special edition ears.

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:02.500
Yes, that's right.

00:07:02.500 --> 00:07:05.500
Hey, do people actually detach it from here?

00:07:05.500 --> 00:07:09.500
I attached this keychain to my bag like this, and...

00:07:09.500 --> 00:07:12.000
No, you're supposed to detach that part.

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:13.500
No, I actually wanted to show this.

00:07:13.500 --> 00:07:15.500
We bought matching keychains too, you know.

00:07:15.500 --> 00:07:17.500
I thought you didn't know how to take it off.

00:07:17.500 --> 00:07:20.500
Of course I do. I've been taking it on and off multiple times today.

00:07:20.500 --> 00:07:23.000
So, we have this headband...

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:27.000
we have this Pal-Palooza themed headband.

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:29.500
Look at it. It's cute, isn't it...

00:07:29.500 --> 00:07:31.500
Cute!

00:07:31.500 --> 00:07:34.000
This is for the thumbnail. A thumbnail candidate.

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:36.500
Ta-da.

00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:39.000
Um... what is this called again?

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:42.000
A stainless steel mug... maybe?

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:44.000
You could call it that, right?

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:47.500
You were saying earlier "I want to buy a cup," right?

00:07:47.500 --> 00:07:49.500
We looked around so many stores,

00:07:49.500 --> 00:07:51.500
And in the end, you chose this one anyway.

00:07:51.500 --> 00:07:53.000
Yeah.

00:07:53.000 --> 00:07:55.500
When I first saw it, I immediately thought
"Oh, this is so cute!"

00:07:55.500 --> 00:07:58.000
But we agreed to check out other stores first,

00:07:58.000 --> 00:08:01.000
so we walked around...

00:08:01.000 --> 00:08:03.500
while riding attractions, and when we went back
to the last souvenir shop...

00:08:03.500 --> 00:08:05.500
...I decided to buy this one.

00:08:05.500 --> 00:08:08.500
Ta-da.

00:08:08.500 --> 00:08:10.500
★ Mickey & Friends Secret Bath Ball

00:08:08.500 --> 00:08:10.500
Bath bomb? Bath ball?

00:08:10.500 --> 00:08:13.500
What character will come out is a surprise! There are 4 types.

00:08:15.500 --> 00:08:18.500
If you have a bath ball, bath time...

00:08:18.500 --> 00:08:20.500
...will be more fun, right?

00:08:20.500 --> 00:08:21.500
That's true.

00:08:21.500 --> 00:08:24.000
As for this one, it's bandaids.

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:25.000
★ Bandaids & Case

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:25.500
An absolute emergency item from earlier!

00:08:25.500 --> 00:08:28.000
Yeah, we were frantically looking for bandaids.

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:31.000
Because we walked a lot, and since I was wearing new shoes,

00:08:31.000 --> 00:08:34.500
my feet got blisters and hurt so much.

00:08:35.500 --> 00:08:38.000
I thought, "Oh no, it's going to hurt more without a bandaid."

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:42.500
So I ended up buying these Baymax bandaids.
The case is squishy and so cute.

00:08:42.500 --> 00:08:44.500
I swear it's cute.

00:08:44.500 --> 00:08:46.500
How do you put them in?

00:08:46.500 --> 00:08:50.000
Maybe you have to fold them first to get them in?

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:51.500
Are you sure... they'll fit?

00:08:51.500 --> 00:08:53.000
Excuse me.

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:54.500
Hello Mr. Baymax.

00:08:54.500 --> 00:08:56.500
Sorry to intrude.

00:08:56.500 --> 00:08:58.500
Sorry it's a bit cramped...

00:08:58.500 --> 00:09:01.000
Wait, is that really how you do it?

00:09:01.000 --> 00:09:02.500
It fits perfectly!

00:09:02.500 --> 00:09:05.500
Ah... ah, wait! It's coming out again.
Okay, okay, I get it. Oh, so that's how.

00:09:05.500 --> 00:09:07.500
If that's the case, then it should be folded differently.

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:11.000
I really don't think that's how you do it.

00:09:11.000 --> 00:09:12.500
It just got all wrinkled.

00:09:12.500 --> 00:09:14.000
Don't worry, it's still usable.

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:17.500
Tomorrow at Disney Sea I'm wearing the same shoes,
so I'm going to put these bandaids on first.

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:20.500
Put them on, and then add...

00:09:20.500 --> 00:09:22.500
Add?

00:09:22.500 --> 00:09:25.000
★ Socks Set

00:09:22.500 --> 00:09:24.000
Ta-da.

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:25.500
Socks.

00:09:25.500 --> 00:09:29.000
With sandals, you know, if this is my foot...
this part causes blisters,

00:09:30.500 --> 00:09:34.500
So we finally bought this when we were about to leave.
To prepare for tomorrow.

00:09:35.500 --> 00:09:38.500
These... are size 19 to 21 centimeters.

00:09:38.500 --> 00:09:40.500
This was the only size left.

00:09:40.500 --> 00:09:43.000
Yeah, the only options were 19-21 cm,

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:45.500
...and 16-18 cm.

00:09:46.500 --> 00:09:49.000
Even though my feet are 23.5 cm...

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:51.000
Well... it stretches if you pull it.

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:52.500
It'll definitely stretch.

00:09:52.500 --> 00:09:54.000
It'll fit if you stretch it a bit.

00:09:54.000 --> 00:09:55.500
Why have we only shown my shopping haul!?

00:09:55.500 --> 00:09:58.000
Well, Anna-chan bought a giant one.

00:09:58.000 --> 00:10:00.000
Anna-chan's haul... can we take it out now?

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:02.000
Come here, come out.

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:04.000
I bought this...

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:07.000
Aaaaa! It's so cuteee!

00:10:08.500 --> 00:10:11.000
I bought a giant plushieeee.

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:13.500
Giant Donald~

00:10:13.500 --> 00:10:16.000
His butt wiggles~. Aaa!

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:20.000
So cute~

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:22.000
I'm cute, aren't I.

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:23.500
Super cute.

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:27.500
The moment we locked eyes, I immediately thought,
"You must be the one."

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:29.500
This child is so sweet.

00:10:29.500 --> 00:10:33.000
His angry face with the little pout is so cute too.

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:35.000
Cuteee.

00:10:35.000 --> 00:10:39.000
Right, when you're an adult you rarely
think about buying plushies.

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:44.000
But since we're in Disney, it's like "Oh, I want one!"
"A place where you can walk around hugging a plushie."

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:46.000
That's true.

00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:49.000
That's why I bought thiiiis!

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:52.500
So, I just bought this one giant item.

00:10:52.500 --> 00:10:55.500
Wow, it's amazing. Donald is cool.

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:58.500
Cute.

00:10:59.000 --> 00:11:00.000
Seriously so cute.

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:15.000
♪ Suddenly singing a love song

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:04.000
Focus on me~

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:08.000
You're so oblivious, you know~

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:11.000
Focus on me~

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:12.500
Tell me that you like me,

00:11:12.500 --> 00:11:13.500
love me~

00:11:13.500 --> 00:11:15.000
Love you!

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:17.000
So cute, right.

00:11:17.000 --> 00:11:18.500
Come here, you.

00:11:18.500 --> 00:11:20.000
So cute.

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:23.000
This is Anna-chan's...

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:25.500
This child.

00:11:25.500 --> 00:11:27.500
I'm going to sleep with him tonight.

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:32.000
Oh yeah, we also met Mickey at the restaurant earlier.

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:34.000
Yeah, we asked for Mickey's autograph.

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:35.500
He gave us his autograph, you know.

00:11:35.500 --> 00:11:37.000
Thank you Mickey!

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:38.500
Thank you~!

00:11:38.500 --> 00:11:41.500
I've never seen Mickey that up close before.

00:11:41.500 --> 00:11:42.500
I'm so happy.

00:11:42.500 --> 00:11:44.000
He was so friendly to everyone.

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:46.000
Yeah, he's such a gentleman.

00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:47.000
An angel.

00:11:47.000 --> 00:11:48.500
I swear he was so cool.

00:11:48.500 --> 00:11:51.000
The food was also all delicious.

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:53.000
